  <name>Tauno Monitor</name>
  <developer_name>Tauno Erik</developer_name>
  <summary>Serial port monitor.</summary>
	<description>
	  <p>It remembers the last settings (Theme, Baud Rate, Port etc), auto reconnects to the serial port and can log data to a file.
Depending on your system you may need to add a user to dialout group to open serial ports:
	    <code>
	      sudo usermod -a -G dialout $USER
	    </code>>
	  </p>
	</description>
